com.cleo.lexicom.beans

Class LexCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cleo.lexicom.beans.LexCommand
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class LexCommand
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    LexCommand is used in conjunction with the IActionController to build/parse/execute commands. Refer to IActionController.parse(String) or IActionController.parse(String) or IHttpResponseListener.put(String[],LexCommand,com.cleo.lexicom.external.HttpRequest,com.cleo.lexicom.external.HttpResponse)
